Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台 DVD 播放机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以借给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和也到了敏感的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多想看的…对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟裕美说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说…说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车站前的电器行\N有很多好看的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这礼拜全部打八折
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你那个要借给学长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他说他没有 DVD 播放机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长你打算看什么样的片子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啦，那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如动作片之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好还有英语的教学软件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有很多种啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看很多种类的，很多种的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DVD 可以简单的选择精彩片段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不必倒带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（成人片）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么，要选哪片好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这片好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安，本须和少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是稔和柚姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来买今天发售的网路游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路连线游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由网际网路连线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和各种人一起玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在网际网路玩游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟很多人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以跟电脑一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以和ちぃ一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有硬件和软件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后跟电脑连接起来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟ちぃ玩電腦遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和要不要玩玩看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你一套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是普及版
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以多附送了一套软件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没有硬件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台 DVD 播放机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以玩网路游戏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去收银台等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和你就慢慢挑选\N那一类的 DVD 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是网路游戏的软件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟稔借的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，利用网际网路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟各种人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟各种人一起玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也可以跟秀樹一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟秀树一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要不要一起玩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ要跟秀樹一起玩網路遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏，游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟秀树玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏，游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟秀树玩游戏\N别急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（请连上网际网路）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路连线？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（请输入登入 ID 及密码）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是登入 ID ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是本须和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的游戏玩了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面尽是写着些我看不懂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没办法开始玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么要登入 ID 跟密码之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你后来有去申请电子信箱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，我没去申请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩网路游戏必须和供应商签约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取得帐号之后才可以玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要到哪里签约？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说明书最后一页
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有供应商的电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先在画面上连到那里看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它说“因您的线路问题无法连线”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你现在正透过\N电话线路和我通电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我一边看说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边想办法试试看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还得花不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个授权费是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个月要一千元？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，第一个月是免费的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宽频接头是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密码错误？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他睡得这么正大光明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密码又错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是网路设定\N你自己搞定好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，就算看说明书我也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（连线成功）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经连上线了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟秀树一起玩游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该一开始就去找新保帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那就马上来开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想回去预习\N明天补习班要上的地方耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天不预习没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下，休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛，来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩，一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了，来了，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏连表情都会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来就像是个菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏会随着我们的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变表情或动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老师，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你的角色\N那么像清水老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我临时做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉上很像而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那张脸\N配那个声音总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，让我们去冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为游戏里可以自由调整大小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏进行时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的机能都会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那ちぃ怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有ちぃ不在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是连到其他伺服器了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你总算连上线了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这游戏对于不同的城镇\N会使用不同的伺服器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉此限制同时上线的玩家人数
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城镇已经客满了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ可能被強制傳送到\N其他城鎮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快去找她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的其他城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为通常有20个伺服器在运作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面又各分成15个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合计共有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓ちぃ孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说菜鸟真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人来玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏会变得很难玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你千万不要做奇怪的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你一个人的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以自由进来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样喜欢说漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国分寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在网路上很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你那个菜鸟好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网路上也有那种没礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间在这里闲聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以多欺少太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑对那些家伙是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔细阅读说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这类的游戏你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我是第一次玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中时因为老是在照顾牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没时间玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样还敢一个人独自冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太鲁莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有那么多恐怖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不能讓ちぃ孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是游戏而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全一副菜鸟样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太鲁莽了，太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存档中）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（存档完毕）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结…结果还是没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我听到了秀树的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有跟秀树在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，今天晚上再玩吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两人的胆子还真大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果今天上课又睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去\N我真的考得上学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个啦，DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像没睡饱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是看到天亮啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没买片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没看过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，这个拿回去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长，这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的秘密收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候还我都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 DVD 的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学长，你借了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是动作片啦，动作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我珍藏的动作片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ大概很期待玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定能一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能天天玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始要拼命读书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来，秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也来玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟秀树一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们今天也在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩才有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要跟ちぃ一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼ちぃ今天還是不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伺服器应该没那么多人才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为人数的关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又跑到其他的城镇去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说如果电脑的性能太强时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会给游戏的伺服器\N带来很大的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会不能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对，不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要乱用魔法的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王终于登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那么强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看杂志和网路上的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没看过有人打倒过他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险，危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过这里就可以到下个城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想不开了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不赢那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜过关）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快帮我倒带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是录影带
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚刚那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像真的是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ打倒了大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以另一个角色的身份出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒无敌的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道ちぃ擁有\N超越伺服器等級的性能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的 CPU 就跟超级电脑同等级…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，不玩游戏了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，因为已经破关了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且ちぃ要是又不見了\N我會很傷腦筋的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒辦法一起玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次再玩别的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩不必连上网路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有别的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个是店长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ，那不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重考生没有暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了读书读书，还是读书
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀树，这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:23:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是海滩阳伞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,义大利是世界的阳伞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是游泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水中的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会受到其所排开的水\N相同重量的浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿，船，喘，串
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在海边啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，去海邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快乐喔

